column4: Frenzied demand for Nvidia's graphic chips shoot prices through the roof
column5: Nvidia Corp's  graphic processors  or GPUs  are so overwhelmingly popular that gamers and cryptocurrency miners are willing to pay up to three times the original list price to get their hands on its cards online.

column4: Frenzied demand for Nvidia's graphic chips shoot prices through the roof
column5: Feb 9 Nvidia Corp's graphic processors  or GPUs  are so overwhelmingly popular that gamers and cryptocurrency miners are willing to pay up to three times the original list price to get their hands on its cards online.

column4: Nvidia's upbeat forecast powered by data center  cryptocurrency demand
column5: Nvidia Corp's  upbeat current-quarter revenue forecast on Thursday underscored surging demand for its graphics chips used in data centers  gaming devices and cryptocurrency mining  sending its shares up as much as 12 percent in extended trading.
